channelRules.sql: SELECT * FROM products WHERE products.product_id IN( SELECT products.product_id FROM products INNER JOIN product_variations ON products.product_id == product_variations.product_id WHERE products.like >= 100 AND ( product_variations.name REGEXP("(.+おやつ.+)|(.+支援.+)") OR  product_variations.price == 0 ) GROUP BY products.product_id HAVING COUNT(*) = ( SELECT COUNT(*) FROM product_variations WHERE product_id = products.product_id ) )
